OL,7,FNine million households have been
OL,8,Furged to send meter readings to their
OL,9,Fenergy supplier as prices rise again,
OL,10,Fwith a further 3% increase forecast
OL,11,Ffor April.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, the average energy bill
OL,14,Ffor households across England,
OL,15,FScotland and Wales has increased by
OL,16,F1.2% after Ofgem raised its price cap
OL,17,Fin response to wholesale prices.
OL,19,FThe increase takes effect just as
OL,20,Ftemperatures are set to plunge, and
OL,21,Fmany face warnings of snow.
