OL,7,FThe latest price cap is 10% or #190
OL,8,Flower than a year earlier, and 57.2%
OL,9,For #2,321 less than during the energy
OL,10,Fcrisis, which was fuelled by Russia's
OL,11,Finvasion of Ukraine in February 2022.
OL,13,FBut it comes as millions of pensioners
OL,14,Fare facing a winter with less support,
OL,15,Fafter the Government decided to scrap
OL,16,Fwinter fuel payments for those who do
OL,17,Fnot receive pension credit or other
OL,18,Fbenefits.
