OL,7,FAbout 10 million pensioners will miss
OL,8,Fout on the payments of up to #300 this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FHouseholds on standard variable
OL,12,Ftariffs (SVTs) who do not have a smart
OL,13,Fmeter should record and submit their
OL,14,Fgas and electricity readings as soon
OL,15,Fas they can to avoid paying for any
OL,16,Fmore energy than they need to at the
OL,17,Fhigher prices.
