OL,7,FUswitch energy spokeswoman Elise
OL,8,FMelville said: "If you leave it any
OL,9,Flater than this, then some of your
OL,10,FDecember energy usage could end up
OL,11,Fbeing estimated and therefore charged
OL,12,Funder the higher January rates.
OL,14,F"Now is also an ideal time to look at
OL,15,Fswitching to a new energy tariff, as
